{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/film-monster-hunter-persenjataan-modern/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Film Monster Hunter Akan Tampilkan Persenjataan Modern?","content":"<p>Kamu mungkin sudah mendengar kabar adaptasi film dari game milik Capcom, yaitu Monster Hunter. Film Monster Hunter ini akan diarahkan langsung oleh Paul W.S. Anderson, pria yang dikenal dengan adaptasi film Resident Evil. Beberapa hari yang lalu telihat beberapa foto dari lokasi syuting yang diambil langsung dari para pemain film. Seperti apakah film Monster Hunter ini? Kalian akan sangat terkejut setelah melihatnya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51573\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51573\" data-attachment-id=\"51573\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-monster-hunter-persenjataan-modern/attachment/01-film-monster-hunter-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-film-monster-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-film-monster-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51573\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"Milla Jovovich mengenakan kostum dalam film Monster Hunter. Sumber: Instagram\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-film-monster-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-film-monster-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51573\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Milla Jovovich mengenakan kostum dalam film Monster Hunter. Sumber: Instagram</p></div>\n<p>Dalam foto instagram milik Milla Jovovich, salah satu pemain dalam film Monster Hunter ini menunjukkan salah satu kostum saat syuting. Terlihat kostum yang dia gunakan seperti sebuah armor yang sedikit modern, tidak ada tema fantasy seperti dalam Monster Hunter. Tapi dari sini kita masih belum tahu apakah kostum ini memang digunakan dalam film nanti atau akan ada penambahan efek CG.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/milla-jovovich-film-monster-hunter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Milla Jovovich Kembali Bintangi Adaptasi Film Game Capcom, Monster Hunter</a></strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51574\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51574\" data-attachment-id=\"51574\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-monster-hunter-persenjataan-modern/attachment/02-film-monster-hunter-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-film-monster-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-film-monster-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51574\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"Film Monster Hunter tampilkan tentara dengan persenjataan modern. Sumber: Instagram\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-film-monster-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-film-monster-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51574\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Film Monster Hunter tampilkan tentara dengan persenjataan modern. Sumber: Instagram</p></div>\n<p>Dan hal yang paling dikhawatirkan pun terjadi. Salah satu aktor dalam film Monster Hunter, yaitu Diego Bonata mengupload foto kondisi langsung dari syuting di instagram miliknya. Dalam fotonya tersebut, Diego menggunakan kostum militer lengkap dengan sebuah senjata rifle. Terlihat bahwa adaptasi film Monster Hunter ini, para pemain akan menggunakan perlengkapan modern sebagai senjata untuk menghabisi monster-monster.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/monster-hunter-sebuah-game-monster-vs-sekelompok-hunter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Monster Hunter: Sebuah Game Monster vs Sekelompok Hunter</a></strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51575\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51575\" data-attachment-id=\"51575\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-monster-hunter-persenjataan-modern/attachment/03-film-monster-hunter-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-film-monster-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-film-monster-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51575\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"Tema fantasi menjadi salah satu ciri khas Monster Hunter. Sumber: Wccftech\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-film-monster-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-film-monster-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51575\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tema fantasi menjadi salah satu ciri khas Monster Hunter. Sumber: Wccftech</p></div>\n<p>Setelah munculnya beberapa foto dari pemain film Monster Hunter di lokasi syuting, banyak fans yang merasa sangat kecewa. Tema fantasy yang menjadi ciri khas Monster Hunter hancur dengan adanya perlengkapan senjata modern. Kekhawatian fans terhadap film ini menjadi kenyataan. Saat pertama kali munculnya berita mengenai Monster Hunter akan diadaptasi menjadi film, banyak fans berspekulasi bahwa film ini akan menjadi standar film action khas Hollywood, seperti Transformers.</p>\n<p>Spekulasi ini menguat setelah nama Paul W.S. Anderson muncul sebagai sutradara dan penulis cerita film Monster Hunter. Belum lagi beberapa nama yang sudah tidak asing lagi dalam film Resident Evil akan ikut serta dalam film ini. Fans menganggap bahwa film ini akan mengikuti jejak film Resident Evil, dimana banyak sekali sumber material penting dalam game yang sering dilewatkan oleh Paul W.S. Anderson.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-resident-evil-transformers-kritik/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sering Dihujat, Film Resident Evil dan Transformers Tetap Laris</a></strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51576\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51576\" data-attachment-id=\"51576\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-monster-hunter-persenjataan-modern/attachment/04-film-monster-hunter-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-film-monster-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-film-monster-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51576\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-film-monster-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"Film Resident Evil dianggap gagal oleh gamer. Sumber: Hellhorror\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-film-monster-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-film-monster-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51576\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Film Resident Evil dianggap gagal oleh gamer. Sumber: Hellhorror</p></div>\n<p>Untuk saat ini film Monster Hunter belum ada informasi mengenai jadwal penayangan di bioskop. Apakah film dari game buatan Capcom ini akan sukses seperti Resident Evil walaupun banyak dikritik oleh fans? Atau justru film ini akan sukses, baik untuk kalangan umum maupun untuk para fans berat Monster Hunter. Seperti apapun filmnya, mari kita tunggu bagaimana Paul W.S. Anderson akan mengeksekusi game Monster Hunter dalam dunia perfilman Hollywood.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/genre/action\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-attachment-id=\"50177\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/karakter-metal-gear-solid-berkesan/attachment/print-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1534763889&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Print&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Banner Komik Action CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-50177\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" alt=\"Banner Komik Action\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4502c4ff-b381-5834-bf51-3246ecb8c99b"}}}